content: User has been seeking employment for nearly 2 years without success and is running out of money. They are currently Ubering with their wife to make ends meet but still struggle to cover expenses. Previously made around 300K but is now looking for roles around 100K. User has approximately 270K in a retirement account and 200-300K in equity in their condo at 505 NE 20th Ave, 203, 33441. They are considering renting or selling the condo and moving to a lower-cost area for financial stability.
